###Hindi hangman

This game is the hindi version of hangman. You have 10 chances to guess the right word
There is a rich feature of jquery user interface powered by google fonts and yeah.. there is stunning audio effects and graphical effects, so please plug in your earphones
while playing this game.

##How to play
You have 10 chances to guess the right word. Click on the hindi alphabets to guess the right word. If it is the wrong word then there will be a error beep sounding and the wrong letter will come under the section of wrong choices. If it is a right letter then there will be a blink sound coming and the blank will be filled with chosen letter.
Have fun!!
